snippet.textDisplay: An to all that think c section is a breeze or “just a quick procedure” it is not. THIS is what a real c section looks like. When I had my son I had a c section. I was in so mich pain I felt then cut me open. Then they drugged me so much I was not awake when I had my son. And I stayed asleep for so long away from my son and my husband was away from me and my son so he thought the worst. 9 hours later I was reunited with them. My recovery took more than 6 months all while being a first time mom. God gave me strength. Shyla you did amazing mommas! Prayers your way, may you heal very soon! 💜
